name: deepfried & triggered
description: it all started back in the orphanage. one day we discovered "pls deepfry" the next day we found "pls triggered" which sent me on a quest. i must find the perfect combination of these two. but how? where? when? do you start on such a journey. the answer is "you just do" so that is what we did. i found the perfect recipe and chose to hide it, inside this cube.
